dialogStrings:
{Yuffie}
“Oh, a dream!
But it felt so real…”

{Cloud}
“Sephiroth! I know you're listening!
I know what you want to say!”

{Cloud}
“That I wasn't in Nibelheim
five years ago.”

{Cloud}
“What you are trying to say is
that you want to confuse me, right?”{PAUSE}“But…even making me see those things
won't affect me."{PAUSE}“I remember it all.
The heat of the fire…the pain in my body…
and in my heart!”

Sephiroth
“Oh, is that so?”{PAUSE}“You're just a puppet…
You have no heart…and cannot feel any pain…”{PAUSE}“How can there be any meaning in the
memory of such a being?”{PAUSE}“What I have shown you is reality.
What you remember, that is the illusion.”

{Cloud}
“But, I want to ask you one thing.
Why…why are you doing this?”

Sephiroth
“Ha, ha, ha…”{PAUSE}“I want to take you back
to your real self.”{PAUSE}“The one who gave me
the Black Materia that day…”

Sephiroth
“Who would have ever thought a failed
experiment would prove so useful?”{PAUSE}“Hojo would die if he knew.”

{Cloud}
“Hojo!? What does he have to do with me?!”

Sephiroth
“Five years ago you were…”{PAUSE}“…constructed by Hojo, piece by piece, right after
Nibelheim was burnt.”{PAUSE}“A puppet made up of vibrant Jenova cells, her
knowledge, and the power of the Mako.”{PAUSE}“An incomplete Sephiroth-clone.
Not even given a number.
…That is your reality.”

{Tifa}
“All that talk of Hojo constructing
you is a lie.”{PAUSE}“We have our memories together, right?”{PAUSE}“Being kids together, starlit nights…”

{Cloud}
“What's wrong, {Tifa}?
I'm not affected by it.”{PAUSE}“…I wasn't paying attention to him.”

Sephiroth
“Ha, ha, ha…{Tifa}…”{PAUSE}“Why are you so worried and scared
by those words?”{PAUSE}“Hmm, shall I show everyone here
what's in your heart?”

Sephiroth
“Ha, ha, ha…
You don't look well.”

{Cloud}
“Why are you so scared?
Don't worry about me. I'm all right.”{PAUSE}“No matter how confused I am,
I'll never believe a word that Sephiroth says.”

{Cloud}
“It's true that sometimes
I can't figure out who I am.”{PAUSE}“There's a lot of things
muddled up in my memories.”

{Cloud}
“But, {Tifa}…”{PAUSE}“But {Cloud}'right?”{PAUSE}“Those words will always support me.”{PAUSE}“I am the one you grew up with.
I'm {Cloud} of Nibelheim.”{PAUSE}“No matter how much faith I lose in
myself, that's the truth.”

{Cloud}
“That's why you shouldn't be so scared.”{PAUSE}“No matter what anyone else says to me,
it's your attitude that counts…”

{Cloud}
“What's not?
I'm the same {Cloud} you
grew up with, aren't I?”

{Tifa}
“That's not what I mean…
I don't know how to say it…”{PAUSE}“{Cloud}, I need some time…
Just give me a little time…”

Sephiroth
“The ability to change one's looks,
voice, and words,
is the power of Jenova.”{PAUSE}“Inside of you, Jenova
has merged with {Tifa}'s
memories, creating you.”

Sephiroth
“Out of the children in {Tifa}'s
memory…”

Sephiroth
“A boy named {Cloud} might've
only been a part of them.”

Sephiroth
“Ha, ha, ha…
Think, {Cloud}!”{PAUSE}“…{Cloud}?
Ha, ha, ha…Oh, excuse me.
You never had a name…”

Sephiroth
“Do you remember the picture that we
took before we headed for the Mt. Nibel?”

Sephiroth
“But there is no way that
he would know.”

Sephiroth
“Do you want to see it?
It turned out pretty good.”

{Cloud}
“I…should be in the picture.”{PAUSE}“Even if I'm not in there, no worry.
This is just an illusory world
Sephiroth made up.”

{Cloud}
“This picture's a fake.
The truth is in my memory.”{PAUSE}“…Five years ago, I came back to Nibelheim,
to inspect the reactor. I was sixteen.”{PAUSE}“The town hadn't changed at all.
What did I do? Oh yeah…”

{Cloud}
“…I didn't have to worry about it,
because I was…”

{Cloud}
“I saw my mom.
I saw the people in town.”

{Cloud}
“Yeah, I went to {Tifa}'s room.
There, I…”

{Cloud}
“I spent the night and went to the reactor
in Mt. Nibel.
I was excited about it.”

{Cloud}
“Because that was my first
mission after becoming First Class in SOLDIER.”
